auto_abilities_data.name: sensor
auto_abilities_data.game_description: View enemy data during battle.
auto_abilities_data.description: Shows enemy HP, elemental resistances, active statuses, and a brief description, while the user is in the active party.

auto_abilities_data.name: piercing
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Deal normal damage to armored enemies.
auto_abilities_data.description: Attacks and skills ignore enemy's Armoured status.

auto_abilities_data.name: first strike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Act first at beginning of battle.
auto_abilities_data.description: Guarantees the first turn during battle even in an ambush.

auto_abilities_data.name: initiative
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Raises party's chances for a preemptive strike.
auto_abilities_data.description: Raises party's chances for a preemptive strike and eliminates ambushes, except against enemys with a 100% ambush rate.

auto_abilities_data.name: firestrike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Adds fire element to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to be fire-elemental.

auto_abilities_data.name: darktouch
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Sometimes adds darkness to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to have a 50% base chance to inflict darkness for three turns. Chance stacks additively with darkstrike.

auto_abilities_data.game_description: Almost always adds darkness to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to have a 100% base chance to inflict darkness for three turns. Chance stacks additively with darktouch.

auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to force the enemy hit to drop Power Spheres. The number of dropped Spheres is equal to the number of items the enemy would have dropped normally.

auto_abilities_data.name: counterattack
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Strike back after being physically attacked.
auto_abilities_data.description: User targets attacker with a counter attack if targeted with a physical attack. Does not trigger against attacks hitting more than one target, nor against attacks that ignore Protect.

auto_abilities_data.name: evade & counter
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Evade physical attack and strike back.
auto_abilities_data.description: If targeted with a physical attack, the user evades the attack, if possible, and then targets attacker with a counter attack. Does not trigger against attacks hitting more than one target, nor against attacks that ignore Protect.

auto_abilities_data.name: magic counter
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Strike back after being attacked with magic.
auto_abilities_data.description: User targets attacker with a counter attack if targeted with a magical attack. Does not trigger against attacks hitting more than one target, nor against attacks that ignore Shell.

auto_abilities_data.name: magic booster
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Use more MP to heighten spell power.
auto_abilities_data.description: Increases the damage and healing of Black and White Magic abilities by 50%, but doubles their MP cost. The MP cost increase stacks multiplicatively with 'Half MP Cost' and 'One MP Cost'.

auto_abilities_data.name: alchemy
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Doubles the potency of recovery items.
auto_abilities_data.description: Recovery items will heal double the normal HP. Does not affect Mix abilities.

auto_abilities_data.name: half mp cost
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Reduces MP cost of spells by half.
auto_abilities_data.description: Reduces the MP cost of all abilities by half. Stacks multiplicatively with Magic Booster.

auto_abilities_data.name: one mp cost
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Reduces MP cost of spells to 1.
auto_abilities_data.description: Sets the MP cost of all abilities by half. Stacks multiplicatively with Magic Booster.

auto_abilities_data.name: double ap
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Doubles the amount of AP earned.
auto_abilities_data.description: Doubles the amount of AP the user receives when in the active party at the time the respective enemy is defeated.

auto_abilities_data.name: triple ap
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Triples the amount of AP earned.
auto_abilities_data.description: Triples the amount of AP the user receives when in the active party at the time the respective enemy is defeated.

auto_abilities_data.name: overdrive -> ap
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Earn more AP instead of charging Overdrive gauge.
auto_abilities_data.description: Converts all Overdrive gauge points obtained by the user to AP while the auto-ability is equipped.

auto_abilities_data.name: sos overdrive
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Charges Overdrive at double speed when HP is low.
auto_abilities_data.description: Doubles the Overdrive charge speed if the user is in HP critical. Doesn't stack with 'Double Overdrive' or 'Triple Overdrive', but does stack with Mix abilities.

auto_abilities_data.name: double overdrive
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Charges Overdrive at double speed.
auto_abilities_data.description: Doubles the Overdrive charge speed. Doesn't stack with 'SOS Overdrive' or 'Triple Overdrive', but does stack with Mix abilities.

auto_abilities_data.name: triple overdrive
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Charges Overdrive at triple speed.
auto_abilities_data.description: Triples the Overdrive charge speed. Doesn't stack with 'SOS Overdrive' or 'Double Overdrive', but does stack with Mix abilities.

auto_abilities_data.name: gillionaire
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Doubles amount of Gil earned.
auto_abilities_data.description: Doubles the amount of Gil earned from battles, if the user is in the active party at the end of the battle.

auto_abilities_data.name: break damage limit
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Allows max damage to exceed 9999.
auto_abilities_data.description: Sets the maximum amount of damage and recovery the character deals to 99,999. This does not affect items or most Mixes.

auto_abilities_data.name: capture
auto_abilities_data.description: Attacks and Skills will capture certain monsters as long as it is the killing blow.

auto_abilities_data.name: no ap
auto_abilities_data.description: The user receives zero AP. Has no effect if the user does not equip the ability at the time the enemy is defeated.
Hidden auto-ability used by Aeons. Grants immunity to all status ailments except Curse and Eject.
